[ProMED-mail thanks Olutayo Babalobi for this news report, which clarifies the location of the meningococcal serogroup A meningitis outbreak to Dungurawa village of Dawakin Tofa Local Government Area in Kano state, Nigeria.

Dawakin Tofa has a population of 247 875 in the 2006 census (https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dawakin_Tofa). A map showing the location of Dungurawa village can be found at http://1worldmap.com/Nigeria/Kano-State/Dungurawa/2592511.

A map of Nigeria that shows the location of its states can be found at http://www.un.org/Depts/Cartographic/map/profile/nigeria.pdf. - Mod.ML

